# X Bookmarks Scraper — Implementation Plan

Build a production-quality Python Playwright automation project to extract bookmarks from X (Twitter), using **uv** for dependency management.

## Proposed Changes

### Project Setup

#### [NEW] [pyproject.toml](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/pyproject.toml)
- Initialize via `uv init`, then `uv add playwright python-dotenv pydantic loguru`
- Run `uv run python -m playwright install` to install browser binaries

#### [NEW] [.env](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/.env)
- Default config: `X_BASE_URL`, `BOOKMARKS_URL`, `DATA_DIR`, `SESSION_FILE`, `HEADLESS`, `SCROLL_DELAY`, `MAX_SCROLL_RETRIES`

---

### Utils

#### [NEW] [utils/logger.py](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/utils/logger.py)
- Configure loguru with file + console sinks, structured format

#### [NEW] [utils/config.py](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/utils/config.py)
- Pydantic `Settings` model loading from `.env` with sensible defaults

