- Generic `retry` decorator with configurable attempts, delay, and exception types

---

### Browser & Session

#### [NEW] [browser/browser_manager.py](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/browser/browser_manager.py)
- Async context manager wrapping Playwright browser lifecycle
- Configurable headless mode via settings

#### [NEW] [browser/session_manager.py](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/browser/session_manager.py)
- Save/load cookies to `session.json`
- Detect login state by checking for known logged-in element

---

### Authentication

#### [NEW] [auth/login_handler.py](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/auth/login_handler.py)
- Prompt for username/password in terminal (using `getpass` for password)
- Automate login via Playwright locators (`data-testid` selectors)
- Handle the username → next → password → submit flow

---

### Navigation

#### [NEW] [navigation/bookmarks_page.py](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/navigation/bookmarks_page.py)
- Navigate to bookmarks URL, wait for `[data-testid="tweet"]`

#### [NEW] [navigation/scroll_manager.py](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/navigation/scroll_manager.py)
- Infinite scroll loop: scroll → wait → count tweets → stop when stable
- Configurable `scroll_delay` and `max_retries`

---

### Data Extraction

#### [NEW] [extractor/tweet_parser.py](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/extractor/tweet_parser.py)
- Extract author, tweet text, tweet URL from each `[data-testid="tweet"]` element

#### [NEW] [extractor/image_parser.py](file:///c:/Users/sksiv/Workspace/ai-agents/x-bookmarks-scraper/extractor/image_parser.py)
- Extract image URLs from tweet media containers

